        GitHub repo: <a href="https://github.com/ayoayco/astro-reactive-form">astro-reactive-form</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        NPM registry: <a href="https://npmjs.org/astro-reactive-form">astro-reactive-form</a>
      </li>
    </ol>
    <Footer />
